{
  "stem": "24346.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have, here, one that I'll show you later, and you'll have it for the record.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were assigned to barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, it was like in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tschenstochova, ?] there, in the munition camp-- big barrack, but this wasn't a stable, because it was set up barracks for prisoners.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the bed, like I say, was four-high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was one bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was another one, so when you came into the barrack, this was full of beds on the right-hand side and full on the left-hand side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The middle was a stove, there, you know, heating, with a pipe going out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the beds were on the right and the left-hand side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was the single bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a four-high, made from wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You could sleep one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Here, we didn't have no straw, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just boards clipped together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And here, already, we slept like sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here, it was crowded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because obviously, they brought too many people in at the same time they had to evacuate, and it was very crowded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Like, you sleep on one side, and you wanted to turn at night, quite a few-- maybe a dozen people-- had to turn, wake up, turn the other side [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's how-- sardines, pressed as sardines in a can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in this camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, I was there about two weeks, and then they sent us to another camp-- from Buchenwald to Dora.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There, already-- again, we went through the same thing-- all the clothing were dropped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A bath-- the same procedure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cutting the hair-- whatever you had, you had to go through that, the same procedure as you arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
